utra]]''{{dagger|alt=Extinct}} (2.6\u20130.12 Mya)\n*** ''N. euxena'' (2.6\u20130.12 Mya)\n** Genus ''[[Paludolutra]]''{{dagger|alt=Extinct}} (8.7\u20133.2 Mya)\n*** ''P. campanii'' (8.7\u20135.3 Mya)\n*** ''P. lluecai'' (5.4\u20133.2 Mya)\n*** ''P. maremmana'' (8.7\u20135.3 Mya)\n** Genus ''[[Sardolutra]]''{{dagger|alt=Extinct}} (2.6\u20130.12 Mya)\n***''S. ichnusae'' (2.6\u20130.12 Mya)\n** Genus ''[[Siamogale]]''{{dagger|alt=Extinct}}\n*** ''[[Siamogale melilutra|S. melilutra]]'' (12\u20134.9 Mya)\n*** ''S. thailandica''\n** Genus ''[[Teruelictis]]''{{dagger|alt=Extinct}} (9.7\u20138.7 Mya)\n*** ''T. riparius'' (9.7\u20138.7 Mya)\n** Genus ''[[Tyrrhenolutra]]''{{dagger|alt=Extinct}}\n*** ''T. helbingi'' (8.7\u20135.3 Mya)\n\n* '''Subfamily Melinae'''\n** Genus ''[[Algarolutra]]''{{dagger|alt=Extinct}} (2.6\u20130.012 Mya)\n*** ''A. majori'' (2.6\u20130.012 Mya)\n** Genus ''[[Arctomeles]]''{{dagger|alt=Extinct}} (11\u20131.8 Mya)\n*** ''A. dimolodontus'' (11\u20131.8 Mya)\n*** ''A. sotnikovae'' (5.4\u20133.6 Mya)\n** Genus ''[[Cyrnolutra]]''{{dagger|alt=Extinct}}\n** Genus ''[[Enhydritherium]]''{{dagger|alt=Extinct}} (14\u20134.9 Mya)\n*** ''[[Enhydritherium terraenovae|E. terraenovae]]'' (14\u20134.9 Mya)\n** Genus ''[[Meles (genus)|Meles]]''\n*** ''M. iberica'' (2.6\u20130.78 Mya)\n*** ''M. thorali'' (2.6\u20131.8 Mya)\n** Genus ''[[Limnonyx]]''{{dagger|alt=Extinct}}\n*** ''L. pontica'' (12\u20135.3 Mya)\n*** ''L. sinerizi''\n** Genus ''[[Megalenhydris]]''{{dagger|alt=Extinct}} (0.13\u20130.012 Mya)\n*** ''M. barbaricina'' (0.13\u20130.012 Mya)\n** Genus ''[[Melodon]]''{{dagger|alt=Extinct}} (16\u20135.3 Mya)\n** Genus ''[[Mionictis]]''{{dagger|alt=Extinct}} (21\u20137.2 Mya)\n*** ''M. angustidens'' (14\u201310 Mya)\n*** ''M. artenensis'' (17\u201315 Mya)\n*** ''M. dubia'' (12\u20137.2 Mya)\n*** ''M. elegans'' (21\u201315 Mya)\n*** ''M. incertus'' (21\u201315 Mya)\n*** ''M. letifer'' (21\u201315 Mya)\n*** ''M. pristinus'' (14\u201310 Mya)\n** Genus ''[[Paralutra